    "These labs typically offer a range of realistic scenarios and hands-on activities that mirror real-world cybersecurity challenges.",
    "Students can experiment with different techniques, tools, and methodologies, gaining practical experience in network security, penetration testing, incident response, and cryptography.",
    "Virtual labs enable students to develop critical thinking, problem-solving, and technical skills necessary for cybersecurity professionals.",
    "This study reveals several challenges in the realm of online learning, accounting for approximately 20% of the articles surveyed.",
    "A notable challenge, as highlighted by Carabantes et al. (2021), was the increased number of student enrolments, which posed difficulties at the beginning of the shift to online education."
